Introduction

An Yujin is a South Korean singer-songwriter and dancer under Starship Entertainment. She is best known as the leader, main dancer and lead vocalist of the girl group IVE.

Yujin was the lead vocalist and lead dancer of the project girl group IZ*ONE; this was made possible after she competed in the hit survival program Produce48 and ranked 5th on the final episode with 280,487 votes.

On November 12, 2021, Yujin was revealed as the sixth and last member of IVE. The group officially debuted on December 1, 2021, with their single album "ELEVEN".
